    <h1>In this project I learned how to display images in different projections</h1>
    
    <h2 style="color:red">Describe in your own words how you displayed the map in different projections using QGIS</h2>
    <p>First, I uploaded the base layer map into QGIS.  To change the projections, I clicked on the projection number in the bottom right corner and clicked the one I wanted.  To add the scaling ?????, I used the indicatrix plugin and ran it on my map.</p>
    
    <h2>WGS84 Projection</h2>
    <h3>Some observations</h3>
